# Images Folder

Place design documentation images here.

## Usage in Markdown

Reference images using absolute paths:

```markdown
![Spellcrafting Scene](/design/images/spellcrafting-scene.png)
![Character Concept](/design/images/character-concept.webp)
```

Or use relative paths from your markdown file:

```markdown
![Local Image](./images/local-image.png)
```

